---
import LayoutBare from "../layouts/LayoutBare.astro";
---

<LayoutBare
  title="Terms & Conditions · Jetski Lefkada Rentals"
  description="Booking terms, cancellation policy and rental conditions for Jetski Lefkada Rentals."
  themeColor="#fdfbf4"
>
  <style>
    body { background: #fdfbf4; color: #0a1220; font-family: "Instrument Sans", ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif; }
    .legal-page { max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 6rem 2rem 4rem; }
    h1 { font-family: "Fraunces Variable", Georgia, serif; font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 1.1; }
    h1 em { font-style: italic; color: #ff5a36; }
    h2 { font-family: "Fraunces Variable", Georgia, serif; font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 400; margin: 2.5rem 0 0.75rem; }
    p, ul, table { font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #2a3a4a; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
    li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    a { color: #00b3a7; text-decoration: none; }
    a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    .back { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #6b7a8d; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
    .back:hover { color: #0a1220; }
    .divider { width: 40px; height: 2px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff5a36, #ffc233); margin: 2rem 0; border-radius: 1px; }
    table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1.5rem 0; }
    th { text-align: left; padding: 0.75rem 1rem; border-bottom: 2px solid #0a1220; font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; }
    td { padding: 0.75rem 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e4da; }
    .warn { background: #fff0ec; border-left: 3px solid #ff5a36; padding: 1rem 1.25rem; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0; margin: 1.5rem 0; }
  </style>

  <div class="legal-page">
    <a href="/v2" class="back">
      <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M19 12H5M11 5l-7 7 7 7"/></svg>
      Back to site
    </a>

    <h1>Terms &<br><em>Conditions</em></h1>
    <div class="divider"></div>

    <h2>1. Booking & Payment</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Bookings are confirmed upon receipt of 30% deposit</li>
      <li>Remaining balance due on the day of rental</li>
      <li>Accepted: Viva Wallet, cash (EUR), card</li>
      <li>Minimum age: 18 years with valid photo ID</li>
      <li>No boating licence required</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. Cancellation Policy</h2>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Notice given</th>
          <th>Refund</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>More than 48 hours before</td><td>100% – full refund</td></tr>
        <tr><td>24–48 hours before</td><td>50% refund</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Less than 24 hours</td><td>No refund</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Weather cancellation (Beaufort 5+)</td><td>100% refund or free rebooking</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2>3. Weather Policy</h2>
    <p>
      We monitor wind conditions every morning. If wind exceeds Beaufort 5, all operations
      are suspended as required by Greek Coast Guard regulations. You will be notified
      as early as possible and offered a full refund or free rebooking.
    </p>

    <h2>4. Safety Rules</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>All operators must complete a 10-minute safety briefing before departure</li>
      <li>Life vest must be worn at all times</li>
      <li>Maximum distance from shore: 700 metres (Greek Coast Guard regulation)</li>
      <li>No entry into marked swimming zones (buoy areas)</li>
      <li>Operating under the influence of alcohol or drugs is strictly prohibited and results in immediate termination without refund</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>5. Liability & Damage</h2>
    <p>
      Third-party liability is covered up to €700,000 per incident (Greek Law 4926/2022).
      Operators are personally liable for damage caused by reckless or prohibited behaviour.
      In case of damage, a written incident report will be completed on site.
    </p>

    <div class="warn">
      <strong>Important:</strong> Personal accident insurance for riders is not included.
      We strongly recommend travel insurance that covers water sports activities.
    </div>

    <h2>6. Force Majeure</h2>
    <p>
      Jetski Lefkada Rentals is not liable for cancellations or delays caused by
      extreme weather, acts of God, or orders from Greek maritime authorities.
    </p>

    <h2>7. Governing Law</h2>
    <p>
      These terms are governed by Greek law. Any disputes shall be subject to the
      exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of Lefkada, Greece.
    </p>

    <div class="divider"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #6b7a8d;">Last updated: April 2026</p>
  </div>
</LayoutBare>
